{
  "stem": "9987.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And within 15 minutes, on September the 1st, 1939, when Germany attacked, about 5 o'clock in the morning, within 15 minutes, the whole, all factories, and the whole-- and we also had an air force stationed in the same town.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was an-- there was an air--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An airfield.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And air field.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Within 15 minutes, everything was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the war started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Poland gave an order that all young people have to withdraw together, to the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, since we live not far from the Carpathian Mountains-- about 15 miles from the Carpathian Mountains-- the German army decided to come to us from Germany, across the Carpathian Mountains from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And within three days, they were in our town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We, as a group of young people, started to withdraw together with the  retreating Polish army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My younger brother, Mike, about a dozen other boys, we were going on foot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were walking for about 150 miles, or rather, kilometers, Not far from Lvov.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Finally, we saw the German tanks started to overrun us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The war was practically finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was no youth running anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we turned around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we started to walk back home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We started to walk back home to Krosno.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "While we were walking back home, we found out that wherever the German came in, the einsetzen troops went after them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And wherever they could find Jews, they killed, with the help of Ukraines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The reason the Ukraines helped out the Germans?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because Germany promised the Ukraines after they will defeat Poland, they will give them an independent state.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Ukraines were very vicious, even worse than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, during the time that we were walking back, we were stopped many times by military police or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
